{"tid":1333414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得我哋仲欠缺咗個旗徽","createTime":"2019-07-19T16:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T00:05:34.000Z","uid":60219,"like":13,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"88b50140564dc62b1ca89276349b0600af944fd1","tid":1333414,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"萬一真係成功成立到臨時組織<br />\n我覺得我哋好需要有自己嘅國旗同國徽<br />\n先至可以顯示到獨立自主嘅決心，更可以激勵更多人企出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yi8rnDV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYi8rnDV.png&h=436a6fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到呢張圖，有小小靈感，就係以雨傘作為國旗同國徽嘅精粹<br />\n希望文宣組可以準備定獨立旗徽，以備不時之需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee03d365ec1f332cdf9a327cde48a6033e0dc5d","tid":1333414,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"黑色洋紫荊"},{"pid":"d87ba96794e0e4f6f50c029e149edd2567399071","tid":1333414,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:37:34.000Z","msg":"唔夠型"},{"pid":"b5b763f69579009c9934b448522da65b4b888663","tid":1333414,"uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;&mdash;&mdash;呢個"},{"pid":"91b6b1fb9a4a414f5187ffe9d4999cfc69f6d763","tid":1333414,"uid":282433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扯晒"},{"pid":"c0766168046f934c2843999cd4d117957e5a6c99","tid":1333414,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d87ba96794e0e4f6f50c029e149edd2567399071","tid":1333414,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:37:34.000Z","msg":"唔夠型"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:58:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾型 又有象徵意義"},{"pid":"f6014875040ad9c1c6b513ec1ec52a1a1b74582b","tid":1333414,"uid":60219,"